data.description: Welcome to 6432 Gander East Road in the neighborhood of Pheasant Hill. You can’t help but just want to make this your HOME once you've walked through the front doors. You’ll find a calm come over you as you move around the circular floor plan on the main level. And when you go upstairs, you’ll be awed by the spacious bedrooms and the spa-like baths. You can enjoy lovely dinners in the formal dining room or have warm conversations while cooking in the eat-in kitchen. Let’s not forget the back deck and gazebo where you can have a cup of coffee in the mornings and great barbecues in the evening. With a big backyard to just enjoy the outdoors. Roof replaced in 2021. All this and you still have a HUGE finished basement great for entertaining. This home is just waiting for you! So what are you waiting for?! Come see your new home today.
